commits.author: Robert Muir
commits.sourceNew:
/** * Checks consistency of this reader. *

* Note that this may be costly in terms of I/O, e.g. * may involve computing a checksum value against large data files. * @lucene.internal */ public abstract void checkIntegrity() throws IOException;
